File Checksum: This is also a great way to detect and verify the integrity of your files. Itâ€™s a huge red flag if the checksum from any file in your server changes without you actively interacting with it.
Backups: Having regular backups of the working version of your website may ease the recovery process just in case something bad happens and you have to revert a specific file.

Cleaning up the Infection
